metadata.name: Lexie The Rottie
metadata.description: FrenchFellas is an NFT collection of 2000 hand-drawn and unique French bulldogs with different properties and rarities. The collection consists of 10 Legendary and 1990 rare/common NFTs, 1900 being males and 100 being female Frenchies. Female Frenchies can mate with up to 10 different males and generate a mint of a baby Frenchie NFT in the 2nd collection. The 2nd collection will only be exclusive to those who own a Frenchie offspring.
